<section class="block" id="trading">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2>From the wholesale market to your meter.</h2>
      <p>Three connected capabilities — trading the markets, supplying the businesses that depend on them, and running the services that keep energy flowing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services">
      <div class="card lead-card reveal">
        <div class="ic" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 17l5-6 4 4 8-9" /><path d="M21 6v5h-5" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Trading</h3>
        <p>We trade across Europe's wholesale energy markets — pricing risk, sourcing volume, and acting quickly when conditions move. Physical and financial, pipeline to terminal.</p>
        <div class="chips">
          <span class="chip">Natural gas</span><span class="chip">LNG</span><span class="chip">Power</span><span class="chip">Environmental products</span><span class="chip">Oil</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 21V8l9-5 9 5v13" /><path d="M9 21v-6h6v6" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Supply</h3>
        <p>Tailored energy for municipal utilities and industrial customers — from steady baseload to the balancing that smooths out the peaks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" /><path d="M12 2v3M12 19v3M2 12h3M19 12h3M5 5l2 2M17 17l2 2M19 5l-2 2M7 17l-2 2" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Services</h3>
        <p>LNG as fuel, balancing-group management and market access — the operational backbone for partners who need a steady hand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
